Description: ==============
        python-delay
        ==============
        
        Simple decorator stolen from stackoverflow to delay function calls.
        
        http://stackoverflow.com/questions/3996083/how-can-i-call-a-function-with-delay-in-python
        
        
        Usage
        ======
        
        from delay import delayed
        
        @delayed(10)
        def foo():
            print "wow"
        
        
